Fractions are NOT:

```text id="r2f8qe"
two
independent
whole numbers
```

Students learn:

```text id="x7f4qe"
represent fraction
→ identify size
→ generate equivalents
→ compare values
→ justify reasoning
```

This develops:

* number sense
* proportional reasoning
* flexibility
* estimation
* algebra readiness

